title: Celebrating Extra-Ordinary Women this International Women's Day
itunes:author: Elizabeth Nyamayaro
description: Contributor(s): Elizabeth Nyamayaro | Dr Christine Chow talks with Elizabeth Nyamayaro about her outstanding leadership in launching one of the world's largest global solidarity movements for gender equality, HeForShe, in addition to her work in the UN and her best-selling book I am a Girl From Africa.
